The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 First Test vs Lanka in Chennai

Chennai: The first match of the three-Test series between Sri Lanka and India will be held here from December 2 to 6. The venue of second and third Tests will be Delhi and Kanpur respectively, Board of Control for Cricket in India secretary S. K. Nair said here on Wednesday. 

As per the request of Sri Lankan board, a warm-up match has been arranged in Bangalore from November 26 to 28, he maintained. The second Test in Delhi will be from December 10 to 14 while the third will be played in Kanpur from December 18 to 22. 

THE ITINERARY 

Nov. 26-28: Warm-up match in Bangalore; Dec 2-6: First Test in Chennai; Dec. 10-14: Second Test in Delhi; Dec. 18-22: Third Test in Kanpur 

